Become a
Member
The Golf Hammock Country Club offers various types of memberships, whether you are a full-time resident of the area, just down for the winter season, or maybe you just want to play in the summer months. Golf Hammock
can offer you the membership that best fits your needs. Golf Hammock can also offer Corporate Memberships.  Give us a call at the Pro Shop and let us help  you become a member at Golf Hammock Country Club today!!!
Pro Shop: 863-382-2151
*Monthly payment plans available*
The above memberships include 15% discount in Pro Shop and use of Golf Hammock driving range
*All prices do not include 7.5% Sales Tax*
